    static public let testData = "[{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Coffee shops are magical places\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Fundamentally, they are spots to caffeinate and enjoy delicious pastries. Many offer much more. Coffee shops are places to be productive and collaborate on side projects. They are places to socialize and meet new people. Most have plenty of seating, plugs to charge your laptop, and wifi. They are open before business offices. They have wonderful ambiance that gets creative ideas flowing.\"}]},{\"type\":\"image\",\"hash\":\"fcbdbc7217824a3ac55009e486878d8c1bc30b6ae1cf37fbaa600e9668aac2f1\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"How it started\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"My infatuation with coffee shops started last year. My friend¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/brandonfancher/\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Brandon Fancher\"}]},{\"text\":\"¬†and I started meeting at our local coffee shop before our day jobs. We worked on a¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://uxdesign.cc/a-crypto-wallet-mvp-and-pivot-f8f43dd15779\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"crytocurrency side project\"}]},{\"text\":\". This started as a weekly routine. Then our work became a daily habit. We had an excuse to leave our houses early, and skip the traffic. We held each other accountable. We started a routine of coffee, code, crypto, and conversation. We got a lot done!\"}]},{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"The best part: friends\"}]},{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"image\",\"hash\":\"ef7994febb500023cb8179de41580469e54ba9046f0233772bed0857b33cc87c\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"We invited our friends,¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://medium.com/u/210e30d2a4c9?source=post_page-----3d0294df7aa7----------------------\",\"children\":[{\"t