]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Turns out, there‚Äôs a lot of time in the morning, if you plan it. Many of us technology and business people work something like 9 to 5. You can make time at the coffee shop, for a side project, paying bills, drawing, or socializing. Maybe it‚Äôs 20 minutes. Maybe it‚Äôs 2 hours, if you‚Äôre really ambitious. It‚Äôs a strangely productive time. Science says we‚Äôre more productive in the morning anyways. But perhaps there‚Äôs more‚Ä¶\"}]},{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Coffee Shop Effect\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://twitter.com/kat_boogaard\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Kat Boogaard\"}]},{\"text\":\", freelance writer, explains how coffee shops boost productivity in her article:¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://blog.trello.com/coffee-shop-effect-boosts-productivity\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"The Coffee Shop Effect\",\"italic\":true}]},{\"text\":\".\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"First, she explains, you are more productive in coffee shops since the brain loves novelty. So being in a new environment, that‚Äôs not your office or house, stimulates the brain, and motivates you to do work.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Second, you can fall victim to unproductive routines in your office. So a coffee shop helps break those routines, which spurs productivity.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Third, going to a coffee shops sets an intent for productivity. The mindful intent to leave the house early for side work shows you‚Äôre already committed.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Finally, coffee shops offer less distractions. There are no office coworkers asking about TPS reports. There are no household chores that need attention.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Oh, and caffeine generally helps with productivity. And coffee shops have plenty.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"image\",\"hash\":\"118981ea1346540b160223da63388c78e178f924d0d2c884da8e3a631c9ab22b\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"\"}]},{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Some cool coffee shop outputs\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Convinced morning coffee helps with productivity and side projects? I am! Here are a few of my own side projects that got¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://uxdesign.cc/a-crypto-wallet-mvp-and-pivot-f8f43dd15779\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"done\"}]},{\"text\":\"¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://uxdesign.cc/march%C3%A9-ux-process-7e3c1651adb0\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"over\"}]},{\"text\":\"¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"https://www.localsideprojects.com/\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"morning\"}]},{\"text\":\"¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"href\":\"http://charlottecoffeeshops.com/\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"coffee\"}]},{\"text\":\".\"}]},{\"type\":\"title\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"How to morning coffee\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Interested in trying morning coffee? Want to experience the¬†\"},{\"text\":\"coffee shop effect\",\"italic\":true},{\"text\":\"?\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"This is how:\"}]},{\"type\":\"orderedList\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"üêì Intentionally wake up 20‚Äì30 minutes earlier, to start.\"}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"üöô Get yourself to a local coffee shop. Preferably one that‚Äôs on the way to work. You may gain some time back, by leaving early, and avoiding traffic.\"}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"‚òïÔ∏è Buy a coffee. Tea works too. And pastries.\"}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"üõ† Open your laptop. Pay some bills. Write a blog post. Start a¬†\"},{\"type\":\"link\",\"